Motorists are urged to exercise caution when traveling in the area as workers and equipment will be working close to traffic.A small rock excavation is scheduled for Friday 8/28/2020. Some sections of the driving lanes (above the new bridge structures) are still gravel/fill material and motorists are advised to slow down and follow the posted speed limits.The contractor’s regular work schedule is Monday through Friday from 6:00AM to 6:00PM.
